                "name": "Deserialization of Untrusted Data"
            },
            "notes": [
                {
                    "category": "summary",
                    "text": "NVIDIA APEX for Linux contains a vulnerability where an unauthorized attacker could cause a deserialization of untrusted data. This vulnerability affects environments that use PyTorch versions earlier than 2.6. A successful exploit of this vulnerability might lead to code execution, denial of service, escalation of privileges, data tampering, and information disclosure.",
                    "title": "Vulnerability description"
                },
                {
